%20post-operative%20complications%2C%20seven%20months%20after%20he%20was%20acquitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20was%20suffering%20from%20gall%20bladder%20infection%20and%20was%20operated%20on%20two%20weeks%20ago%20in%20Nizam's%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(NIMS)%2C%20but%20developed%20complications%20subsequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20daughter%20Manjeera%20told%20PTI%20Videos%20that%20he%20had%20Covid%20twice%2C%20his%20health%20was%20in%20abysmal%20condition%20while%20he%20was%20in%20jail%20and%20he%20recovered%20every%20time.%20Hence%2C%20she%20said%20that%20family%20was%20hoping%20that%20he%20would%20come%20back%20this%20time%20too.%20Neither%20Saibaba%20nor%20family%20members%20expected%20his%20death%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20expressed%20hope%20during%20the%20last%20conversation%20she%20had%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Manjeera%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20body%20had%20borne%20too%20much%20all%20these%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20miss%20him.%20I%20still%20cannot%20believe%20he%20is%20not%20with%20us.%20I%20still%20feel%20that%20I%20will%20go%20and%20open%20the%20door%20and%20he%20will%20be%20there%20sitting%20on%20his%20wheelchair%20telling%20me%20to%20do%20this%20and%20that.%20I%20still%20feel%20that%20way.%20I%20still%20feel%20that%20he%20is%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Manjeera%20said%20they%20were%20aware%20that%20his%20condition%20was%20severe%20since%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20but%20at%20around%208%20pm%2C%20doctors%20told%20the%20family%20that%20his%20heart%20had%20stopped%20beating%20and%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20perform%20CPR%20on%20him.%20They%20pronounced%20him%20dead%20at%208.30%20last%20night%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20was%20terminated%20from%20service%20by%20the%20DU%20and%20his%20official%20accommodation%20was%20taken%20away%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba's%20death%20will%20contin