0said%2C%20were%20the%20ones%20who%20had%20enlisted%20two%20of%20the%20shooters%2C%20Dharmaraj%20Kashyap%20and%20Shiv%20Kumar%20Gautam%2C%20in%20the%20plot.%20While%20Gautam%20is%20on%20the%20run%2C%20Kashyap%20was%20arrested%20on%20Saturday%20and%20he%20claimed%20in%20a%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20is%20a%20minor.%20Since%20his%20Aadhaar%20card%20states%20that%20he%20is%2019%2C%20the%20court%20has%20ordered%20a%20bone%20ossification%20test%20to%20ascertain%20his%20real%20age.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%2C%20Pravin%20had%20written%20that%20Siddique%20had%20been%20murdered%20because%20he%20was%20linked%20to%20India's%20most%20wanted%20terrorist%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%2C%20was%20close%20to%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20because%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Anuj%20Thapan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20arrested%20suspects%20in%20the%20shooting%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%20in%20April%2C%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20any%20enmity%20with%20anyone%20but%20whoever%20helps%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20the%20Dawood%20gang%2C%20keep%20your%20accounts%20in%20order%20(%3Cem%3E'hisaab-kitaab%20kar%20lena'%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20now%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20Shiv%20Kumar%20Gautam%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20the%20alleged%20handler%20of%20the%20three%20shooters%2C%20Mohammad%20Zeeshan%20Akhtar%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20hiding%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bishnoi%20gang%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20kill%20Salman%20Khan%20because%20of%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20shooting%20blackbucks%20at%20Bawad%20in%20Mathania%20near%20Jodhpur%20in%20September%201998%2C%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20%3Cem%3E'Hum%20Saath%20Saath%20Hain'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20alleged%20act%20had%20upset%20the%20Bishnoi%20community%2C%20which%20considers%20the%20blackbuck%20sacred.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A172883886