onicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fover-155-000-applicants-register-on-internship-portal-within-a-day-124101300459_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fover-155-000-applicants-register-on-internship-portal-within-a-day-124101300459_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fover-155-000-applicants-register-on-internship-portal-within-a-day-124101300459_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThose%20Who%20Help%20Salman%20Khan...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gang's%20Warning%20After%20Baba%20Siddique%20Killing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20has%20not%20only%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Baba%20Siddique%20but%20also%20threatened%20that%20anyone%20who%20helps%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20near%20whose%20house%20it%20has%20already%20fired%20warning%20shots%2C%20will%20be%20in%20its%20crosshairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Mr%20Siddique%2C%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20and%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%2C%20was%20killed%20near%20the%20office%20of%20his%20son%2C%20MLA%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%2C%20in%20Bandra%20East%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20speculation%20began%20swirling%20of%20a%20Bishnoi%20gang%20link%20to%20the%20daring%20crime.%20This%20was%20confirmed%20on%20Sunday%20after%20a%20post%20on%20Facebook%20by%20one%20Shubuu%20Lonkar%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20Bishnoi%20gang%20associate%20Shubham%20Rameshwar%20Lonkar%2C%20claiming%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Lonkar%20is%20in%20jail%2C%20police%20said%20the%20post%20was%20made%20by%20his%20brother%20Pravin%20Lonkar%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20Sunday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%2C%20Lonkar%20claimed%20that%20Siddique%20had%20been%20killed%20because%20he%20was%20linked%20to%20India's%20most%20wanted%20terrorist%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%2C%20was%20close%20to%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20because%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Anuj%20Thapan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20arrested%20suspects%20in%20the%20shooting%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%2C%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThapan%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20May%201%20inside%20the%20Mumbai%20Crime%20Branch%20lock-up.%20The%20police%20had%20said%20he%20died%20by%20suicide%20but%20his%20family%20had%20claimed%20he%20was%20tortured%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20any%20enmity%20with%20anyone%20but%20whoever%20helps%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20the%20Dawood%20gang%2C%20keep%20your%20accounts%20in%20order%20(%3Cem%3E'hisab-kitaab%20kar%20lena'%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%26quot%3B%20Lonkar%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%20in%20the%20Facebook%20post.%20Police%20said%20they%20are%20verifying%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%20was%20known%20for%20hosting%20lavish%20parties%20and%20a%20five-year-long%20cold%20war%20between%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20was%20resolved%20at%20his%20'iftar'%20party%20in%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20at%20least%20two%20celebrities%20have%20been%20attacked%20by%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20for%20their%20perceived%20closeness%20to%20Salman%20Khan%20since%20last%20year.%20Mr%20Khan%20visited%20the%20hospital%20where%20Siddique%20was%20admitted%20after%20he%20was%20shot%20on%20Saturday%20and%20also%20went%20to%20his%20residence%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20shots%20were%20fired%20at%20the%20house%20of%20Punjabi%20singer%20Gippy%20Grewal%20in%20Canada's%20Vancouver%20and%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20had%20said%20it%20had%20done%20so%20because%20Mr%20Grewal%20had%20praised%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20treated%20him%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20brother%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Grewal%20had%20said%20he%20had%20only%20met%20the%20actor%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20this%20year%2C%20shots%20were%20fired%20near%20the%20house%20of%20another%20Punjabi%20singer%2C%20AP%20Dhillon%2C%20in%20Vancouver.%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20a%20notorious%20member%20of%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20had%20said%20the%20shooting%20was%20the%20handiwork%20of%20the%20outfit.%20The%20firing%20occurred%20after%20Mr%20Dhillon%20released%20a%20video%20of%20his%20song%20%3Cem%3E'Old%20Money'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20featured%20Salman%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Salman%20Khan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20which%20became%20a%20household%20name%20after%20claiming%20responsibility%20for%20murdering%20musician%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20in%202022%2C%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20kill%20Salman%20Khan%20because%20of%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20shooting%20blackbucks%20at%20Bawad%20in%20Mathania%20near%20Jodhpur%20in%20September%201998%2C%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20%3Cem%3E'Hum%20Saath%20Saath%20Hain'%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20act%20had%20upset%20the%20Bishnoi%20community%2C%20which%20considers%20the%20blackbuck%20sacred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%20had%20said%20during%20a%20court%20appearance%20in%202018%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20kill%20Salman%20Khan%20in%20Jodhpur.%20Everyone%20will%20know%20once%20we%20take%20action.%20I%20have%20not%20done%20anything%20as%20of%20now%2C%20they%20are%20accusing%20me%20of%20crimes%20for%20no%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHeightened%20Security%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20security%20has%20been%20tightened%20around%20Salman%20Khan's%20house%20-%20Galaxy%20Apartments%20in%20Bandra%20-%20outside%20which%20a%20firing%20had%20taken%20place%20on%20April%2014.%20Mr%20Khan%20had%20later%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20believed%20that%20the%20shooting%20was%20done%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20killing%20him%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tight%20security%20cordon%20has%20also%20been%20put%20in%20place%20in%20South%20Mumbai's%20Malabar%20Hill%2C%20where%20the%20residences%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20are%20located.%20Siddique%2C%20who%20had%20been%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%20for%2048%20years%2C%20had%20switched%20to%20Mr%20Pawar's%20party%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20patrolling%20has%20been%20increased%20in%20the%20Malabar%20Hill%20area%20and%20some%20points%20have%20also%20been%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728836820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F6iu2m6b8_salman-khan-_625x300_07_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-who-help-salman-khan-lawrence-bishnoi-gangs-warning-after-baba-siddique-killing-6779824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20has%20not%20only%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20Baba%20Siddique%20but%20also%20threatened%20that%20anyone%20who%20helps%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20near%20whose%20house%20it%20has%20already%20fired%20warning%20shots%2C%20will%20be%20in%20its%20crosshairs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-who-help-salman-khan-lawrence-bishnoi-gangs-warning-after-baba-siddique-killing-6779824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Shocking%20and%20monumental%20in%20scale'%3A%20UK%20woman%20sentenced%20to%20life%20after%20killing%20parents%2C%20living%20with%20bodies%20for%20four%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728835510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114194201%2Cimgsize-1174559.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fshocking-and-monumental-in-scale-uk-woman-sentenced-to-life-after-killing-parents-living-with-bodies-fo