height%3D%5C%223411%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle's%20share%20of%20US%20advertising%20could%20drop%20below%2050%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20more%20than%2010%20years%2C%20according%20to%20eMarketer.%3Cp%3EDilara%20Irem%20Sancar%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20is%20facing%20new%20competition%20in%20the%20advertising%20market%20as%20AI%20transforms%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle's%20search%20ad%20market%20share%20in%20the%20US%20could%20fall%20below%2050%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPerplexity%20AI%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20says%20it%20is%20attracting%20%26quot%3Btop-tier%26quot%3B%20advertisers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20facing%20a%20challenge%20to%20its%20decadeslong%20dominance%20of%20the%20internet's%20advertising%20market%20as%20AI%2C%20the%20new%20kid%20on%20the%20block%2C%20changes%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProjections%20by%20eMarketer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20digital%20marketing%20research%20company%20owned%20by%20Business%20Insider%20parent%20company%20Axel%20Springer%20%E2%80%94%20say%20that%20Google's%20share%20of%20the%20US%20search%20advertising%20market%20could%20drop%20below%2050%25%20next%20year%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20dominant%2C%20Google%20has%20begun%20to%20slip%20in%20other%20significant%20ways%20too.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-losing-status-as-verb-genz-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20younger%20generations%2C%20like%20Gen%20Z%20and%20Gen%20Alpha%2C%20are%20no%20longer%20using%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BGoogle%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20verb.%20Young%20internet%20users%20are%20now%20%26quot%3Bsearching%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BGoogling%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Shmulik%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Bernstein%20Research%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20to%20investors%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20is%20due%20in%20part%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20AI%20tools%20like%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20Perplexity%20AI%2C%20which%20use%20large%20language%20models%20trained%20on%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data%20to%20answer%20user%20questions%20in%20natural%20language.%20ChatGPT%20set%20the%20record%20for%20the%20fast-growing%20user%20base%20for%20a%20consumer%20application%20soon%20after%20it%20first%20launched%20in%20late%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENever%20to%20be%20outdone%2C%20Google%20has%20raced%20to%20catch%20up.%20It%20launched%20Gemini%2C%20its%20own%20large%20language%20model%20that%20now%20presents%20Google%20search%20results%20in%20natural%20language%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20page%2C%20in%20March%202023.%20Google%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-layout-changing-generative-ai-more-traffic-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolled%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-lens-ai-gemini-overviews-new-features-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseries%20of%20other%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20tools%20and%20enhancements%20to%20its%20search%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20also%20leveraging%20AI%20to%20better%20present%20ads%20in%20its%20search%20results.%20It%20demonstrated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fads-commerce%2Fgoogle-lens-ai-overviews-ads-marketers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20example%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20showing%20how%20Tide%20products%20are%20now%20advertised%20below%20a%20search%20query%20for%20%26quot%3Bhow%20do%20I%20get%20grass%20stains%20out%20of%20jeans%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20confident%20in%20this%20approach%20to%20monetizing%20our%20AI-powered%20experiences%2C%26quot%3B%20Brendon%20Kraham%2C%20a%20Google%20vice%20president%20overseeing%20the%20search%20ads%20business%2C%20told%