will%20be%20portrayed%20in%20an%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20opening%20up%20is%20the%20ability%20for%20a%20brand%20to%20spark%20or%20inspire%20somebody%20to%20ask%20a%20question%20about%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Shevelenko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20and%20Perplexity%20AI%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20requests%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-ad-market-share-perplexity-ai-openai-chatgpt-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728833877000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6702f53e3f2165d716debe1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-ad-market-share-perplexity-ai-openai-chatgpt-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20is%20facing%20new%20competition%20as%20AI%20transforms%20the%20advertising%20market%20and%20its%20cultural%20dominance%20wanes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-ad-market-share-perplexity-ai-openai-chatgpt-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Terrifier%203%E2%80%99%20Tops%20Box%20Office%20With%20%2418%20Million%20Debut%2C%20%E2%80%98Joker%3A%20Folie%20%C3%A0%20Deux%E2%80%99%20Collapses%20With%20Brutal%2081%25%20Drop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728833752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FTERRIFIER-3_6.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236176346%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%E2%80%99s%20only%20room%20for%20one%20killer%20clown%20at%20the%20top%20of%20box%20office%20charts.%20%E2%80%9CTerrifier%203%E2%80%9D%