0even%20when%20its%20rockets%20blow%20up%20spectacularly%2C%20has%20ultimately%20accelerated%20development%20and%20contributed%20to%20the%20company's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20only%20in%202002%2C%20it%20quickly%20leapfrogged%20aerospace%20industry%20giants%20and%20is%20now%20the%20world%20leader%20in%20orbital%20launches%2C%20besides%20providing%20the%20only%20US%20spaceship%20currently%20certified%20to%20carry%20astronauts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20created%20the%20world's%20biggest%20internet%20satellite%20constellation%20--%20invaluable%20in%20disaster%20and%20war%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20founding%20vision%20of%20making%20humanity%20a%20multiplanetary%20species%20is%20increasingly%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20overshadowed%20by%20Musk's%20embrace%20of%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20alignment%20with%20right-wing%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20the%20company%20has%20openly%20sparred%20with%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20over%20launch%20licensing%20and%20alleged%20violations%2C%20with%20Musk%20accusing%20the%20agency%20of%20overreach%20and%20calling%20for%20its%20chief%2C%20Michael%20Whitaker%2C%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20trying%20to%20position%20himself%20for%20minimal%20regulatory%20interference%20with%20SpaceX%20once%20Donald%20Trump%20becomes%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Hass%2C%20a%20marketing%20expert%20and%20professor%20at%20Arizona%20State%20University.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20a%20calculated%20gamble%20if%20things%20go%20the%20other%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728831720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fq8bv9tno_spacex-starship-booster_625x300_13_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%2