i%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAllen%20Onyema%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Nigeria's%20Air%20Peace%20airline%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20obstruction%20of%20justice%20in%20the%20US%2C%20adding%20to%20previous%20charges%20of%20bank%20fraud%20and%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20press%20release%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-ndga%2Fpr%2Fceo-nigerian-airline-and-co-defendant-indicted-obstruction-justice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20Georgia%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20Onyema%2C%2061%2C%20was%20charged%20with%20%26quot%3Bsubmitting%20false%20documents%20to%20the%20government%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20end%20an%20investigation%20of%20him%26quot%3B%20that%20led%20to%20those%20earlier%20charges%2C%20which%20were%20brought%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEjiroghene%20Eghagha%2C%2042%2C%20Air%20Peace's%20chief%20of%20administration%20and%20finance%2C%20was%20also%20charged%20with%20obstruction%2C%20the%20press%20release%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20were%20indicted%20in%202019%20over%20allegations%20that%20they%20had%20moved%20more%20than%20%2420%20million%20from%20Nigeria%20through%20US%20bank%20accounts%20by%20using%20false%20documents%20based%20on%20the%20purchase%20of%20five%20Boeing%20737%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20says%20they%20submitted%20export%20letters%20of%20credit%20to%20fund%20the%20purchases%2C%20along%20with%20supporting%20purchase%20agreements%2C%20bills%20of%20sale%2C%20and%20appraisals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20prosecutors%20argue%20that%20these%20documents%20were%20fake%20and%20that%20the%20company%20supposedly%20selling%20the%20planes%2C%20the%20Georgia-registered%20firm%20Springfield%20Aviation%2C%20was%20owned%20by%20Onyema%20and%20managed%20by%20someone%20with%20no%20connection%20to%20the%20aviation%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aircraft%20that%20was%20refe