ss%20prodigy%20as%20a%20child.%3Cp%3ESergey%20Peterman%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20became%20interested%20in%20chess%20at%20the%20age%20of%20four%20while%20watching%20his%20father%20play%20against%20his%20uncle%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fdeepmind%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Wired%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Two%20weeks%20later%2C%20Hassabis%20was%20beating%20adults%20at%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20age%20of%20five%2C%20he%20was%20competing%20nationally.%20He%20won%20the%20London%20under-eights%20championships%20at%20six%20years%20old.%20When%20he%20was%20nine%2C%20he%20was%20captaining%20England's%20under-11%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2013%2C%20Hassabis%20reached%20the%20rank%20of%20chess%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHassabis%20bought%20his%20first%20computer%20when%20he%20was%208%20years%20old%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22487%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ZX%20Spectrum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670816b56ac7b701e7ca29cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHassabis%20became%20interested%20in%20computers%20at%20a%20young%20age.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Macdiarmid%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHassabis%20bought%20his%20first%20computer%20with%20money%20he%20won%20from%20a%20chess%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amazing%20thing%20about%20computers%20in%20those%20days%20is%20you%20could%20just%20start%20programming%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fdeepmind%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHassabis%20told%20Wired%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20go%20with%20my%20dad%20to%20Foyles%2C%20and%20sit%20in%20the%20computer%20programming%20department%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20give%20myself%20infinite%20l