20families%3B%20it%20just%20wasn't%20great%20for%20toddlers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20realized%20this%20was%20typical%20of%20family-friendly%20resorts%20%E2%80%94%20while%20they%20had%20great%20amenities%20for%20older%20kids%2C%20they%20just%20weren't%20built%20for%20very%20young%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20hotels%20that%20market%20themselves%20as%20family-friendly%20are%20actually%20focused%20on%20school-aged%20children.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediocre-clubmed-wed-go-back-to-for-the-childcare-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKids'%20clubs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20terrific%20amenity%20for%20families%20with%20older%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20are%20typically%20for%20ages%205%20and%20up.%20Other%20family-marketed%20activities%2C%20like%20water%20sports%2C%20appeal%20to%20tweens%20and%20teens.%20After%20much%20futile%20searching%20for%20a%20hotel%20that%20was%20suited%20to%20toddlers%2C%20I%20switched%20approaches.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ea47182-fd95-4ad2-9168-836a2377072d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20we%20stay%20at%20luxury%20resorts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20I%20opt%20for%20luxury%20hotels%2C%20which%20are%20sometimes%20no%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20big%20resorts%20marketed%20to%20families.%20As%20for%20toddler-focused%20amenities%2C%20every%20luxury%20hotel%20I've%20encountered%20has%20the%20basics%20%E2%80%94%20a%20crib%20or%20pack%20'n'%20play%20available%2C%20along%20with%20a%20mini%20fridge%20either%20standard%20or%20on%20request.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnything%20else%20I%20need%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20pack%20(my%20SlumberPod%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%20bulky%20beach%20toys)%2C%20I%20rent%20through%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-of-3-shares-best-tips-travel-little-kids-2022-7%5C%22%20t