cs-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20best%20friend%20is%20moving%20across%20the%20country%20for%20a%20new%20job%2C%20and%20while%20I'm%20pretending%20to%20feel%20happy%20for%20her%2C%20I'm%20hurt%20that%20she%20is%20choosing%20to%20leave%20me%20for%20a%20new%20life%20and%20new%20friends.%20I%20can't%20imagine%20a%20world%20where%20traveling%20to%20see%20her%20is%20regularly%20doable%20due%20to%20the%20cost.%20Should%20I%20tell%20my%20friend%20how%20I%20feel%20or%20keep%20pretending%20not%20to%20mind%20to%20be%20supportive%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbandoned%20for%20Ambition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Abandoned%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20ago%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20part%20of%20a%20three-couple%20friend%20group.%20But%20then%2C%20one%20of%20the%20couples%20announced%20they%20were%20moving%20away%20to%20the%20coast.%20We%20were%20devastated%2C%20but%20we%20understood%2C%20so%20we%20told%20ourselves%20and%20each%20other%20that%20we%20were%20%3Cem%3Eso%3C%2Fem%3E%20happy%20for%20them.%20The%20third%20couple%20in%20our%20friend%20group%20did%20not%20understand.%20They%20were%20hurt%20and%20upset%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20spend%20nearly%20as%20much%20time%20feigning%20delight%20for%20our%20other%20friends%20as%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20their%20unapologetic%20sense%20of%20place%20in%20our%20friends'%20lives%20bizarre.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20their%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20would%20tell%20my%20husband%2C%20aghast.%20%26quot%3BThey%20aren't%20going%20to%20choose%20monthly%20dinners%20and%20the%20odd%20lunch%20date%20over%20their%20dream%20lives!%26quot%3B%20But%20deep%20down%2C%20I%20was%20envious%20of%20our%20bitter%20friends'%20confidence%20in%20their%20entitlement%20because%20it%20was%20much%20more%20honest%20than%20the%20Jokerish%20smile%20I%20wore%20at%20the%20going%20away%20party%20and%20my%20squeaky%20pleas%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20so%20many%20pictures%20of%20your%20new%20place%20and%20send%20them%20to%20me!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20you%20may%20read%20my%20advice%20in%20this%20letter%20and%20realize%20I%20still%20think%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20more%20right%20than%20our%20bitter%20friends%2C%20I%20want%20to%20say%20from%20the%20jump%20that%20your%20self-awareness%20and%20self-honesty%20are%20admirable.%20You%20can%20only%20understand%20your%20feelings%20if%20you%20are%20honest%20with%20yourself%20about%20what%20they%20are.%20Your%20experience%20of%20your%20friend's%20choice%20to%20move%20is%20valid.%20Where%20it%20ranks%20on%20the%20list%20of%20importance%20in%20another%20person's%20whole%20life%20is%20another%20question%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20make%20the%20hurt%20you%20feel%20mean%20any%20less%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20not%20all%20emotional%20expression%20is%20constructive.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20being%20honest%20with%20your%20friend%2C%20whether%20that%20honesty%20means%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20miss%20you%20desperately%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20even%20%26quot%3BThis%20might%20take%20some%20time%20for%20me%20to%20get%20used%20to.%20I%20imagined%20us%20living%20as%20roomies%20in%20the%20retirement%20home%20someday%2C%26quot%3B%20keep%20your%20love%20for%20your%20friend%20front%20and%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsk%20yourself%20what%20you%20really%20want%20out%20of%20this%20situation.%20Obviously%2C%20you%20want%20nothing%20to%20change%20and%20your%20bestie%20to%20stay%20nearby%20forever%2C%20but%20when%20you%20think%20about%20her%20best%20interests%20%E2%80%94%20a%20burgeoning%20career%2C%20new%20adventures%2C%20personal%20growth%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20sure%20what%20you%20really%20want%20is%20her%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20even%20as%20you%20are%20honest%20with%20your%20friend%20about%20your%20feelings%2C%20make%20sure%20she%20understands%20that%20your%20feelings%20aren't%20her%20job.%20Her%20job%20is%20to%20embark%20on%20this%20exciting%20new%20life%20and%20make%20it%20everything%20you%20want%20for%20her.%20This%20will%20mean%20focusing%20less%20on%20your%20heartbreak%20and%20more%20on%20her%20plans.%20Even%20better%2C%20make%20plans%20to%20keep%20this%20friendship%20alive%20despite%20the%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20friends%20of%20ours%20who%20moved%20to%20the%20coast%3F%20We're%20still%20friends.%20They%20still%20visit%20us%2C%20and%20we%20make%20it%20a%20financial%20priority%20to%20fly%20out%20to%20see%20them%20once%20a%20year.%20We%20downloaded%20apps%20like%20Marco%20Polo%20to%20keep%20the%20day-to-day%20nature%20of%20our%20friendship%20alive%3B%20we%20text%20each%20other%20articles%2C%20DM%20funny%20videos%2C%20watch%20games%20simultaneously%2C%20and%20keep%20each%20other%20updated%20on%20our%20reactions.%20We%20constantly%20talk%20about%20the%20podcast%20we're%20unlikely%20to%20ever%20make%20with%20one%20another.%20We're%20millennials%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20talk%20on%20the%20phone%20much%2C%20but%20when%20something%20big%20happens%2C%20we%20make%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20friendship%20has%20changed%2C%20but%20you%20know%20what%20it%20hasn't%20done%3F%20It%20hasn't%20faded.%20No%20one%20decided%20they%20didn't%20like%20the%20other%20and%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out.%20Our%20friends%20simply%20chose%20an%20awesome%20job%20opportunity%20in%20a%20gorgeous%20place%20and%20imagined%20a%20fantastic%20future%20for%20themselves%2C%20and%20then%20they%20went%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20It%20was%20never%20about%20our%20friendship%2C%20so%20it%20didn't%20need%20to%20impact