vember%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDate%20of%20Examination%3A%20December%207%2C%208%2C%2014%2C%20and%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESWAYAM%20is%20a%20program%20introduced%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20tailored%20to%20achieve%20the%20three%20key%20principles%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy-access%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20quality.%20The%20initiative%20aims%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20teaching-learning%20resources%20to%20all%2C%20including%20the%20underprivileged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seeks%20to%20bridge%20the%20digital%20divide%20for%20students%20who%20have%20yet%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20digital%20era%20and%20who%20are%20not%20fully%20integrated%20into%20the%20knowledge-driven%20economy.%20SWAYAM%20offers%20online%20certification%20courses%20in%20various%20subjects%2C%20with%20exams%20conducted%20every%20semester%20either%20in%20Computer-Based%20Mode%20or%20a%20hybrid%20mode%20combining%20CBT%20and%20traditional%20paper-and-pen%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTA%20has%20been%20entrusted%20with%20overseeing%20the%20SWAYAM%20exam%20for%20the%20July%202024%20semester%2C%20covering%20a%20total%20of%20456%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728801180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fogledbvg_swayam-portal_625x300_05_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnta-swayam-july-2024-registration-begins-official-website-swayam-nta-ac-in-6778459%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NTA%20has%20been%20entrusted%20with%20overseeing%20the%20SWAYAM%20exam%20for%20the%20July%202024%20semester%2C%20covering%20a%20total%20of%20456%20courses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnta-swayam-july-2024-registration-begins-official-website-swayam-nta-ac-in-6778459%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lumi%C3%A8re%E2%80%99s%20Classic%20Fi