n.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%20aware%20of%20how%20futile%20it%20would%20prove%20to%20uproot%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F135175%2Ftamil-nadu-sanitary-napkin-incinerators-government-schools-promoting-menstrual-hygiene%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewell-entrenched%20custom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20and%20her%20husband%20Dr%20Abhay%20Bang%20(74)%20decided%20to%20revamp%20it%20instead.%20With%20intervention%20from%20the%20Mukul%20Madhav%20Foundation%2C%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20couple%20built%20new%20versions%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20ghar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecomplete%20with%20modern%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Johns%20Hopkins%20to%20Gadchiroli%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20scan%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20list%20leaves%20me%20in%20a%20dilemma.%20It%20boasts%2072%20individual%20accolades%20of%20national%20and%20international%20repute%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20%E2%80%98Maharashtra%20Bhushan%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20conferred%20by%20the%20State%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra%3B%20the%20first%20ever%20Distinguished%20Alumnus%20Award%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20International%20Health%2C%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%3B%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Award%3B%20the%20ICMR%20award%3B%20a%20shortlist%20as%20%E2%80%98Global%20Health%20Heroes%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20TIME%20Magazine%20(2005)%3B%20and%20%E2%80%98Public%20Health%20Champion%E2%80%99%20by%20WHO%20(2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20effort%20of%20Dr%20Rani%20and%20Dr%20Abhay%20%E2%80%94%20ex-chairman%20of%20the%20Expert%20Committee%20for%20Tribal%20Health%2C%20appointed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20frame%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190299%2Fmaharashtra-doctor-couple-hospital-tribal-community-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%