%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-3-1728467967-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369365%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Rani%20Bang%20is%20an%20MD%20in%20obstetrics%20and%20gynaecology%20and%20specialises%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20health.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20their%20opinion%2C%20scanty%20or%20normal%20menstruation%20indicates%20that%20the%20blood%20is%20collecting%20in%20the%20uterus%2C%20forming%20lumps%2C%20and%20will%20eventually%20impinge%20on%20their%20vital%20organs%20and%20cause%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20proper%20diagnoses%20extends%20to%20children%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20as%20well%2C%20she%20figured.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20we%20started%20working%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F116337%2Fgood-news-india-averted-million-child-deaths-since-2005%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfant%20mortality%3C%2Fa%3E%20rate%20was%20121%20per%201%2C000%20(indicating%20that%20121%20out%20of%201%2C000%20children%20would%20die%20before%20reaching%20the%20first%20year%20of%20life).%20The%20number%20one%20cause%20was%20childhood%20pneumonia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20she%20along%20with%20Dr%20Abhay%20trained%20the%20village%20health%20workers%20to%20diagnose%20and%20treat%20the%20condition.%20This%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20by%2060%20percent.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20model%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%2C%20UNICEF%20and%20all%20the%20international%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20is%20evidently%20proud%3B%20the%20model%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%2016%20countries%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20They%20realised%20that%2060%20percent%20of%20infant%20deaths%20are%20due%20to%20sepsis.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20started%20educating%20village%20health%20workers%20%E2%80%98Aarogya%20Doot%E2%80%99%20(Health%20Messengers)%20to%20detect%20and%20treat%20neonatal%20infections.%20This%20brought%20down%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20to%2020%20per%201%2C000.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducate%20adolescents%20about%20sex%20education%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346145%2Ftermination-of-pregnancy-act-india-dr-nikhil-datar-case-legal-battle-to-raise-abortion-limit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECriminal%20abortions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20highlights%2C%20are%20not%20just%20atrocities%20limited%20to%20tribal%20areas.%20Their%20grip%20extends%20to%20rural%20villages%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CSticks%20and%20local%20herbs%20are%20inserted%20inside%20the%20uterus%20causing%20contractions.%20The%20patient%20is%20forced%20to%20abort%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20explains.%20Though%20resulting%20in%20the%20desired%20outcome%2C%20the%20sticks%20are%20infective%2C%20causing%20sepsis%20to%20set%20in%20and%20subsequent%20death.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20need%20for%20these%20reductive%20and%20out-of-touch%20procedures%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20highlights.%20%E2%80%9CSince%201971%2C%20India%20has%20legalised%20abortions%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(MTP)%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-4-1728468093.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20the%20health%20advocacy%20sessions%20that%20Dr%20Rani%20conducts%20in%20the%20villages%20across%20Gadchiroli%2C%20crucial%20health%20problems%20are%20addressed%20as%20well%20as%20prevalent%20gaps%20in%20medical%20care%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-4-1728468093.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-4-1728468093-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-4-1728468093-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-4-1728468093-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-4-1728468093-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369367%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20health%20advocacy%20sessions%20that%20Dr%20Rani%20conducts%20in%20the%20villages%20across%20Gadchiroli%2C%20crucial%20health%20problems%20are%20addressed%20as%20well%20as%20prevalent%20gaps%20in%20medical%20care.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shares%20a%20horrifying%20discovery%20proving%20that%20criminal%20abortions%20are%20true%20to%20their%20name%20for%20more%20reasons%20than%20one.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20procedures%20were%20usually%20done%20by%20male%20%E2%80%98quacks%E2%80%99%20who%20would%20extract%20money%20from%20the%20woman%20and%20her%20family.%20Post%20the%20procedure%2C%20they%20would%20indulge%20in%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20with%20the%20woman%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F91667%2Fdurgaiah-throat-cancer-survivor-fight-tobacco-addiction%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvocacy%20programmes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20urges%20doctors%20and%20medical%20workers%20to%20take%20cognisance%20of%20these%20outmoded%20sensibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrain%20more%20doctors%20to%20conduct%20caesareans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20remember%20the%20very%20first%20case%20that%20you%20dealt%20with%3F%20I%20ask%20Dr%20Rani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20memory%2C%20I%20deduce%2C%20is%20perfect%2C%20as%20she%20recalls%20being%20called%20upon%20by%20the%20district%20hospital%20to%20attend%20to%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20in%20distress.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20labour%20was%20obstructed%20and%20prolonged.%20I%20checked%20for%20foetal%20heart%20sounds%2C%20they%20were%20absent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-5-1728468177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gadchiroli%20now%20has%20trained%20nurses%20and%20healthcare%20practitioners%20who%20can%20perform%20C-sections%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20lower%20maternal%20mortalities%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-5-1728468177.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-5-1728468177-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe