0chosen%20life%20partner%E2%80%99s%20destructive%20behaviour.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20would%20not%20only%20beat%20me%20but%20also%20force%20himself%20on%20me%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20years%20went%20by%2C%20the%20abuse%20escalated%2C%20and%20Ambika%20found%20herself%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20for%20their%20two%20daughters.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20stopped%20paying%20rent%20for%20our%20home%20and%20would%20not%20even%20give%20me%20money%20to%20buy%20milk%20for%20our%20six-month-old%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20provide%20financial%20support%20left%20her%20burdened%20with%20the%20sole%20responsibility%20of%20sustaining%20their%20household.%20She%20started%20balancing%20a%20demanding%20job%20at%20a%20book-binding%20company%20and%20caring%20for%20her%20two%20daughters.%20While%20she%20was%20pushed%20to%20her%20limits%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally%2C%20the%20violence%20at%20home%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20eight%20years%20until%20one%20day%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20him%20to%20pay%20at%20least%20for%20the%20groceries%2C%20but%20he%20started%20beating%20me.%20I%20cried%20myself%20to%20sleep%20but%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20woke%20up%20the%20next%20day%2C%20he%20again%20started%20beating%20me.%20I%20was%20exhausted%20of%20this%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ambika%2C%20adding%20that%20that%20was%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20end%20her%20suffering%20by%20taking%20her%20own%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20poured%20some%20kerosene%20on%20me%20and%20set%20myself%20on%20fire.%20When%20my%20neighbours%20saw%20me%20burn%2C%20I%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital.%20I%20sustained%2034%20percent%20burn%20injuries%20on%20my%20body.%20The%20scars%20were%20deep.%20Even%20now%20I%20have%20burn%20marks%20on%20my%20right%20parts%20of%20the%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20Ambika%E2%80%99s%20story%20of%