r%20India.%20Editorial%20integrity%20and%20transparency%20remain%20our%20priority%2C%20and%20this%20piece%20has%20been%20written%20independently%20to%20provide%20an%20unbiased%20view.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20truly%20comprehend%20the%20vast%20economic%20potential%20brimming%20in%20India%2C%20visit%20its%20rural%20heartlands%20%E2%80%93%20like%20driving%20through%20the%20villages%20of%20Hubbali%20district%20in%20Karnataka.%20As%20you%20negotiate%20the%20twists%20and%20turns%20of%20the%20road%2C%20notice%20how%20the%20verdant%20landscape%20is%20punctuated%20with%20shops%2C%20now%20and%20then.%20A%20closer%20look%20will%20reveal%20barcodes%20displayed%20in%20plain%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20new%20addition%2C%20as%20shop%20owner%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday%20mornings%20are%20a%20busy%20time%20for%20him%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(general%20store)%20that%20he%20runs.%20But%20Ishwargowda%20seems%20unfazed%20by%20the%20slew%20of%20orders.%20He%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20required%20to%20ace%20mental%20math%20while%20attempting%20to%20calculate%20the%20amount%20of%20change%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20returned%20to%20a%20customer.%20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface)%20has%20his%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20fascinating%20to%20watch%20the%20rhythmic%20order%20of%20business%20%E2%80%94%20with%20transactions%20happening%20in%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20picture%20of%20a%20new%20age%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BUPI%5D%20makes%20things%20hassle-free%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishwargowda%20points%20out.%20However%2C%20building%20a%20successful%20business%20requires%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20integrating%20tech%20into%20transactions%2C%20he%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20loans%20too.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20where%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20rural%20lending%20startups%20comes%20into%20play.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20an%20