ccording%20to%20NCRB%20data%2C%20cybercrime%20cases%20in%20India%20rose%20significantly%2C%20jumping%2063.48%25%20from%2027%2C248%20in%202018%20to%2044%2C548%20in%202019.%20This%20trend%20continued%20with%20a%20further%20increase%20of%2012.32%25%20in%202020.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20UNICEF%20poll%20revealed%20that%20over%2033%25%20of%20young%20people%20across%2030%20countries%20have%20reported%20being%20victims%20of%20online%20bullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirali%20Bhatia%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20Ritesh%20Bhatia%2C%20have%20been%20helping%20victims%20of%20cyberbullying%20since%202016%20and%20elaborates%20on%20the%20problem.%20Together%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F179257%2Fmumbai-couple-troll-police-cyberbullying-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20run%20CYBER%20B.A.A.P%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20an%20acronym%20for%20%E2%80%9CCyberbullying%20Awareness%2C%20Action%2C%20and%20Prevention%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20their%20brainchild%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20organisation%20registered%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Niralibhatia%20Cyber%20Wellness%20Foundation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHonestly%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20specific%20redressal%20mechanism%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F107128%2Ffreedom-of-speech-in-the-age-of-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecyberbullying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20se%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20pointing%20out%20two%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20women%20may%20face%20when%20trying%20to%20fight%20cyberbullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNumber%20one%2C%20we%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20all%20the%20sections%20it%20%5Bcyberbullying%5D%20falls%20under%2C%20or%20how%20to%20report%20it.%20Number%20two%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20guilt%20and%20shame%20associated.%20Because%20even%20police%20professionals%20are%20not%20yet%20sensitised%20towards%20these%20kinds%20of%20crimes.%20The%20first%20question%20is%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20did%20you%20even%20click%20a%20picture%20like%20this%3F%E2%80%99%20That%20itself%20takes%20you%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Pritha%2C%20both%20these%20roadblocks%20were%20a%20reality.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20issue%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20young%20guys%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20the%20communication%20she%20received%20when%20she%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20cyber%20crime%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20I%20really%20had%20no%20clue.%20But%20I%20was%20losing%20sleep%3B%20I%20began%20losing%20some%20confidence.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20recalls%3B%20she%20pauses%2C%20perhaps%20trying%20to%20subdue%20the%20trauma%20that%20some%20men%2C%20hiding%20behind%20computers%2C%20scarred%20her%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%2C%20who%20was%20my%20then%20partner%2C%20was%20the%20one%20who%20told%20me%20that%20this%20is%20cyberbullying%20and%20that%20I%20can%20lodge%20a%20complaint%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20followed%20up%20(with%20the%20cyber%20department)%20for%20three%20months%2C%20but%20nothing%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20900px)%20100vw%2C%20900px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Pritha%20it%20was%20a%20traumatic%20experience%20that%20pushed%20her%20the%20avoid%20social%20media%20for%20a%20while.%20for%20Priya%2C%20to%20be%20am%20influencer%20social%20media%20was%20her%20tool.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media