d%20impersonate%20her%20and%20chat%20with%20people.%20She%20started%20getting%20these%20random%20calls.%20So%20she%20reported.%20She%20told%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20they%20went%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20They%20knew%20someone%2C%20and%20the%20profile%20was%20deleted.%20But%20the%20problem%20continued.%20When%20one%20profile%20was%20deleted%2C%20another%20one%20opened%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20girl%20reached%20out%20to%20Nirali%2C%20and%20she%20recalls%20taking%20down%2016%20to%2017%20such%20profiles%20of%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20other%20day%2C%20an%20acquaintance%20sent%20me%20an%20account%20with%20my%20photo.%20It%20had%20my%20face%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20nude%3B%20a%20morphed%20picture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%20But%20the%20number%20of%20times%20Priya%20has%20found%20herself%20in%20such%20instances%20has%20made%20her%20indifferent%20today%3B%20she%20has%20her%20life%20to%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20point%20I%20was%20like%2C%20okay%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20clarify%20it%20on%20my%20personal%20account%2C%20and%20ask%20everybody%20to%20report%20it.%20And%20most%20times%20it%20gets%20deleted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20checked%20after%20it%20four%20days%20later%20and%20the%20profile%20was%20deleted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143543%2Ffacebook-ncw-women-internet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Instagram%20have%20the%20option%20to%20make%20a%20profile%20private.%20Nirali%20says%20that%20it%20is%20an%20important%20preventive%20step.%20But%20for%20some%20people%2C%20a%20private%20profile%20might%20not%20be%20an%20option.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20point%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20so%20indifferent%20about%20it%20because%20as%20someone%20with%20a%20public%20account%20%E2%80%94%20I%20