0year%2C%20we%20will%20start%20exporting%20to%20other%20countries.%20A%20lot%20of%20companies%20are%20working%20on%20agriculture%20residues%20to%20make%20products%2C%20but%20our%20zero-waste%20approach%20helps%20us%20stand%20out%20in%20the%20market.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagat%2C%20Satyam%2C%20and%20Nitish%20are%20not%20only%20entrepreneurs%20but%20also%20champions%20of%20sustainable%20innovation%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20greener%20future%20and%20a%20more%20inclusive%20economy.%20Their%20initiative%20showcases%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20positive%20change%20by%20reimagining%20waste%20as%20a%20valuable%20resource%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20circular%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20dedication%20and%20vision%2C%20Taruwar%20demonstrates%20that%20small%20actions%20can%20lead%20to%20significant%20impacts%2C%20inspiring%20others%20to%20embrace%20sustainability%20and%20community%20empowerment%20in%20their%20entrepreneurial%20endeavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20switch%20from%20the%20corporate%20world%20to%20a%20purpose-driven%20journey%2C%20Jagat%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20was%20hesitant%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20job.%20After%20you%20invest%20your%20time%20and%20efforts%20in%20pursuing%20higher%20education%20in%20engineering%20and%20an%20MBA%2C%20anyone%20can%20expect%20you%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20high-paying%20job.%20But%20after%20the%20initial%20doubts%2C%20they%20understood%20where%20my%20true%20calling%20was%20and%20extended%20their%20support.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20banana%20waste%20in%20a%20radius%20of%2010%20kilometres%20from%20our%20factory%20is%20being%20used%20as%20raw%20materials%20for%20useful%20products.%20With%20this%2C%20farmers%20are%20also%20getting%20extra%20monetary%20benefits.%20Banana%20waste%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20headache%20for%20them%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Ar