market%20is%20very%20competitive.%20Nobody%20wants%20the%20other%20person%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20them.%20This%20is%20why%20our%20journey%20to%20make%20the%20workplace%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20more%20inclusive%20starts%20at%20the%20leadership%20level%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20are%20going%20to%20promote%20and%20help%20women%20come%20back%20and%20rejoin%20the%20workforce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20helps%20companies%20to%20hire%20more%20women.%20But%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20they%20ask%20companies%20to%20give%20their%20women%20applicants%20only%20remote%20working%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20asking%20them%20to%20establish%20exclusive%20policies%20to%20hire%20women%20but%20inclusive%20ones.%20Speaking%20to%20companies%2C%20we%20explain%20to%20them%20why%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20also%20give%20women%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20same%20role%20as%20they%20give%20men.%20Unlike%20days%20in%20the%20past%2C%20women%20today%20also%20travel%20and%20do%20night%20or%20second%20shifts%20while%20technology%20has%20upgraded%20and%20companies%20have%20the%20salary%20cap%20space.%20So%2C%20why%20not%20hire%20more%20capable%20women%20instead%20of%20leaving%20them%20out%3F%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20particularly%20unique%20about%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20that%20they%20are%20focused%20on%20delivering%20well-experienced%20talent%20for%20tech%20companies%20with%20a%20turnaround%20time%20of%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20venture%20is%20looking%20to%20diversify%20the%20workplace%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-1-1728052022-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20(Image%20courtesy%20yurakrasil%2Fshutterstock)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20get%20a%20requirement%20from%20a%20company%2C%20we%20give%20them%20matching%20job%20profiles%20within%2024%20hours.%20Following%20this%2C%20you%20have%20the%20standard%20hiring%20process%20by%20a%20company.%20Once%20the%20company%20completes%20their%20rounds%20of%20tests%20and%20interviews%2C%20the%20person%20who%20is%20selected%20joins%20the%20company%20within%20a%20day.%20We%20are%20focussed%20on%20delivering%20the%20right%20job%20(for%20the%20candidate)%2C%20and%20the%20right%20candidate%20(for%20the%20company)%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20job%20profiles%2C%20we%20are%20focused%20on%20project%20managers%2C%20designers%2C%20mobile-based%20application%20developers%2C%20web-based%20application%20developers%2C%20the%20front%20end%2C%20back%20end%2C%20full%20stack%20developers%2C%20testers%2C%20etc.%20We%20want%20women%20to%20have%20more%20opportunities%20in%20tech%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20current%20state%20of%20women%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20that%20are%20hiring%20talent%20through%20the%20robust%20online%20community%20they%20have%20developed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EShework.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20offers%20a%20platform%20called%20%3Cem%3ETech%20Pundit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20connects%20mentors%20and%20mentees%20for%20personalised%20guidance%20and%20learning%20experiences.%20When%20we%20have%20tech%20mentors%20talking%20to%20women%20in%20our%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20community%2C%20we%20help%20them%20navigate%20the%20latest%20trends%20in%20technology%20and%20what%20skills%20they%20currently%20lack.%20Through%20our%20community%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20them%20up-skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20regularly%20hearing%20catchphrases%20like%20%E2%80%98diversity%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98diversity%20hiring%E2%80%99%20during%20recruitment%20drives%20by%20various%20companies%2C%20Pooja%20observes%20that%20they%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20women%20equal%20pay%20despite%20having%20the%20requisite%20skill%20set.%20That%20is%20a%20major%20challenge%20they%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20still%20have%20to%20convince%20companies%20to%20upgrade%20their%20salary%20packages%20for%20women.%20If%20companies%20offer%20a%20person%20a%20certain%20job%20profile%20because%20they%20are%20capable%2C%20they%20should%20also%20pay%20them%20accordingly.%20That%20is%20something%20which%20I%20feel%20is%20still%20lacking%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20hire%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20person%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Project%20Lead%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20are%20doing%20so%20because%20they%20find%20their%20skill%20sets%20appropriate.%20As%20a%20company%2C%20they%20are%20not%20hiring%20talent%20because%20they%20want%20to%20fill%20up%20some%2