.%20Were%20there%20wild%20beasts%20lurking%20inside%3F%20Or%20something%20more%20ferocious%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20it%20sounds%20like%20an%20excerpt%20from%20one%20of%20Grimm%E2%80%99s%20Fairy%20Tales%2C%20the%20incident%20is%20a%20real-life%20scene%20that%20awaited%20Pallab%20Roy%20(60)%20and%20his%20family%20when%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310006%2Froyal-sisters-duo-akshita-mrinalika-the-belgadia-palace-boutique-hotel-odisha-sustainable-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevisited%20their%20ancestral%20palace%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kasim%20Bazar%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20300-year-old%20architecture%20had%20fallen%20into%20a%20state%20of%20despair%20since%20its%20last%20occupant%2C%20Pallab%E2%80%99s%20grandfather%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%2C%20passed%20away%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPallab%20has%20my%20unwavering%20attention%20as%20he%20narrates%20his%20story%2C%20a%20tale%20that%20takes%20me%20back%20to%20an%20Enid%20Blyton%20adventure.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20his%20parents%20Prosanta%20Kumar%20and%20Supriya%20Roy%2C%20his%20wife%20Sudeshna%2C%20his%20son%20Saurav%2C%20and%20his%20daughter-in-law%20Priya%2C%20would%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20take%20upon%20them%20the%20arduous%20task%20of%20restoring%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20turn%20this%20spectral%20ruin%20into%20a%20liveable%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%3A%20Battling%20snakes%20and%20lizards%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20approaching%20one%20room%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20says%20as%20he%20recalls%20the%20renovation%20process.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20only%20when%20%E2%80%98operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%20commenced%20that%20the%20family%20could%20ascertain%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20devastation.%20The%20years%20of%20isolation%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20royal%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsects%2C%20five-inch%20thick%20layers%20of%20dust%20and%20crumbling%20roofs%20marred%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20restore%20what%20had%20once%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341653%2Funique-homestay-in-goa-maharashtra-sawantwadi-palace-hotel-run-by-royal-family-sawant-bhonsle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esymbol%20of%20grandeur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20was%20infested%20with%20snakes%20and%20monitor%20lizards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20exclaims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20is%20an%2018th%20century%20marvel%20in%20Murshidabad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366171%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20is%20an%2018th-century%20marvel%20