%20by%20termites.%20Even%20some%20of%20the%20supporting%20beams%20were%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20recalls.%20The%20cleaning%20spree%20went%20on%20for%20years%2C%20yielding%20three%20rooms%20that%20were%20deemed%20fit%20to%20live%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20ancestral%20palace%20into%20a%20guesthouse.%20However%2C%20Pallab%20explains%20that%20the%20plan%20flopped%20as%20social%20media%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20popular%20back%20then%20and%20most%20people%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20guest%20house.%20It%20seemed%20like%20the%2018th-century%20palace%20would%20remain%20desolate.%20Unable%20to%20watch%20their%20ancestral%20pride%20meet%20such%20a%20fate%2C%20the%20Roy%20family%20decided%20to%20rebuild%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332940%2Fdevpur-royal-homestay-darbargadh-in-kutch-jadeja-family-runs-farmstay-cbse-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20soon%20become%20a%20heritage%20hotel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Buckingham%20of%20India%E2%80%99%3A%20Reviving%20a%20lost%20legacy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20heyday%2C%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20would%20have%20earned%20the%20%E2%80%98Buckingham%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20moniker.%20Explaining%20the%20comparison%2C%20Pallab%20shares%20that%20the%20palace%E2%80%99s%20functioning%20was%20in%20tune%20with%20colonial%20times%20and%20its%20practices%20mirrored%20those%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%20in%20England.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20British%20Government%20had%20a%20system%20of%20administering%20estates%20through%20the%20Court%20of%20Wards%20if%20the%20person%20in%20power%20was%20a%20minor%20and%20the%20guardian%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20present.%20Across%20the%2010%20generations%20of%20our%20family%2C%20three%20generations%20have%20seen%20their%20owners%20die%20young.%20And%20so%2C%20for%20almost%2045%20years%2C%20the%20British%20Government%20administered%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20%E2%80%93%20who%20lost%20his%20father%20at%20the%20age%20of%20six%20months%20%E2%80%93%20was%20brought%20up%20by%20a%20British%20governess%20for%20six%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-2-1726573228.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20has%20been%20restored%20to%20its%20former%20glory%20and%20is%20now%20a%20plush%20heritage%20hotel%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-2-1726573228.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-2-1726573228-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-2-1726573228-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-2-1726573228-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-2-1726573228-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366175%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20has%20been%20restored%20to%20its%20former%20glory%20and%20is%20now%20a%20plush%20heritage%20hotel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%